---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact | Nordic Coffee">
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-24">
            <h1 class="text-display font-medium text-ink mb-6">Contact</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-ink-muted">
                取材のご依頼、イベントのご相談はこちらから。
            </p>
        </header>

        <form class="space-y-12">
            <!-- Name -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <label
                    for="name"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40"
                    >Name</label
                >
                <input
                    type="text"
                    id="name"
                    name="name"
                    class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-ink/10 py-4 focus:border-accent outline-hidden transition-colors duration-300 text-ink"
                    placeholder="お名前（必須）"
                    required
                />
            </div>

            <!-- Email -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <label
                    for="email"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40"
                    >Email</label
                >
                <input
                    type="email"
                    id="email"
                    name="email"
                    class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-ink/10 py-4 focus:border-accent outline-hidden transition-colors duration-300 text-ink"
                    placeholder="メールアドレス（必須）"
                    required
                />
            </div>

            <!-- Message -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <label
                    for="message"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40"
                    >Message</label
                >
                <textarea
                    id="message"
                    name="message"
                    rows="6"
                    class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-ink/10 py-4 focus:border-accent outline-hidden transition-colors duration-300 text-ink resize-none"
                    placeholder="お問い合わせ内容をご記入ください。"
                    required></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-8">
                <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="w-full md:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-ink text-canvas text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] rounded-nordic hover:opacity-90 transition-all duration-300"
                >
                    Send Message
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>

        <p class="mt-16 text-[10px] text-ink-muted leading-loose">
            ※通常、2〜3営業日以内にご返信を差し上げております。お急ぎの場合はお電話にてお問い合わせください。
        </p>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
